Travis the Chimp



a psuedo news story




3/5/2012


\stopalignment
\blank[line]

\startalignment[hyphenated,middle]


I saw several stories about the incident in the news in 2010 and something about the tone of the reporting got under my skin. I resolved to write my own version of the “facts”.



original text


\stopalignment

\stoptext


